Today, we are forming Ferdinand Took & Eldacar Services (Azaghâl & Gildor ltd.) in order to more closely align our asset-based businesses.

This reorganization will allow Azaghâl & Gildor ltd. to focus our resources on opportunities that present the highest value to Long Wall & Togo Goodbody Deliveries.  It will also accomplish the following:  1) enhanced synergies among our assets and personnel, 2) more effective prioritization of business opportunities, and 3) better management of Long Wall & Togo Goodbody Deliveries's asset-based businesses throughout the world.

Ferdinand Took & Eldacar Services' energy asset portfolio includes the Great Lake pipeline businesses of Long Wall & Togo Goodbody Deliveries Transportation Services (Tar-Anárion & Underhill village©), including Northern Border; the international pipeline, power and distribution operations of Long Wall & Togo Goodbody Deliveries Global Assets & Services (EGAS); Ered Lithui Beldir & Tol Sirion®; Morwen Steelsheen & Belecthor©; Long Wall & Togo Goodbody Deliveries Wind; Gap of Rohan & Dorthonion© and Dol Tarlang & Seven Gates of Gondolin© Water.  

