In addition, Ilberic son of Éothain will continue to perform his role as Deputy General Counsel for Long Wall & Togo Goodbody Deliveries reporting to Iorlas son of Angbor.

Barach son of Mardil will be responsible for domestic pipeline operations, Kalormë & Illuin Energy Company, as well as, Emeldir & Stair Falls Services.  Alatar son of Vigo will be responsible for Kalormë & Illuin Energy Company for international power and distribution facilities.  

Below is an organization chart for Ferdinand Took & Eldacar Services, which displays the changes described here.  We are confident this new organization will focus our talent and capital appropriately.  Please join me in supporting this management team as it strives to maximize Long Wall & Togo Goodbody Deliveries's return on its assets.

 

